*Model Part Num: 90IG0020-BM3000
===Overview=== *Ethernet WAN allows to use as an DSL modem router :or stand-alone wireless router *Compatible with VDSL2, ADSL2/2+, fiber and cable services :for complete future-proofing *Four independent SSIDs for flexible and secure Wi-Fi :network configuration *Fast Ethernet ports for the reliable internet performance *PPTP VPN server and PPTP/L2TP VPN client support *VDSL/ADSL WAN multi service for IPTV support
===Specifications=== :per ''ASUS'''s product page *Memory: Flash: 16MB; RAM: 64MB (DDR2) *Antenna: 2x external 2dBi antenna *Ports: xDSL: 1x ADSL2+ (RJ11) :LAN: 4x FE (RJ45) 10/100 BaseT *Power Adapter: :AC Input : 100~240V (50~60HZ) :DC Output : 12V / 0.5A *Dimensions (W x H x D): [[Dimensions::190 mm x 35 mm x 235 mm]] *Weight: [[Weight::225 g]]
